images.caption: Figure 1:The FullStack-Agent system. It combines a multi-agent development framework equipped with efficient coding and debugging tools (FullStack-Dev), an iterative self-improvement method that enhances LLMs through repository augmentation and back-translation (FullStack-Learn), and a comprehensive benchmark evaluating frontend, backend, and database functionalities (FullStack-Bench).
